    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This didn't go into matplotlib, so I don't think we should be adding it to a list of known backends in IPython. If it's possible to provide an external backend for matplotlib, we should make sure IPython will work with any available mpl backend, but we shouldn't do that by adding code for each individual one we know about.\n"
